A WORD FROM
THE PRESIDENT
Civic, business and industrial leaders
recognize that time saving aerial commuter
service has become essential to the move.
ment of people in metropolitan areas.
Surface streets and freeways alone can no
longer handle the traffic volume.
Aero Commuter has been one of the
nation's leaders in developing the type of
commuting that expedites travelers to their
destinations. Short-haul aerial commuting
is becoming a way of life throughout Cali-
fornia and our company is happy to be a
vital force in the continuing development
of this type of service.
Mird
Haku
Capt. Fred Austin
